{"tid":2056860,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【反修例一周年】林鄭：初心無變 我無攸錯 搞咁多嘢一切都係為左潘生潘太","createTime":"2020-06-09T03:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T12:16:30.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"477eb3bdfbc3f898bcc142adf258e395051fa8e6","tid":2056860,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T03:57:30.000Z","msg":"記者問到她如何看待「賣港」批評，林鄭一度哽咽落淚，稱自己與所有香港人一齊成長，對於這個地方她作出不少犧牲。<br />\n她又指其丈夫林兆波不理政事和世事，但他也認為「賣港」二字有問題，又稱林兆波對她說：「你點可能賣港呢，但你真係有問題，你做行政長官之後，就真係賣咗個身畀香港。」<br />\n至於會否落台，她說：「我從來冇因為呢件事有任何心虛，我哋工作，初心仍然係堅實嘅，認為係啱嘅，不但對受害人家屬有所交代，我𠵱家只可以講話有得交代，但唔能夠答應潘太（受害人母親）將謀害佢哋女兒嘅人繩之於法。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/8AdVTL4hrC4/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F8AdVTL4hrC4%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=05af374f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52548f5ae590938c7d90fedc66337c42926f9cec","tid":2056860,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T04:00:14.000Z","msg":"賣港賊 初心不變 繼續賣港<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>國際線抗爭動畫上線啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2055151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2055151</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8f2d7475fe7eab153b2230850f6aa8b263087901","tid":2056860,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T04:05:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"539f40619618a58eeb41b6f32ebe0c9d39bb83de","tid":2056860,"uid":75664,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T04:08:34.000Z","msg":"咁點解陳同佳依家仲嘆緊世界？"},{"pid":"e82df5a72ddc2c34a8596083973deb62173345db","tid":2056860,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T09:31:46.000Z","msg":"攸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個字點讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 悠<img src=\"/assets/